data.value:
· If there is a delay in any zone of any duration, it will be considered as hours to recover, all the time.
· If there is an early departure in any zone of any duration, it will be considered as hours to recover, all the time.
· If there is an excess in any zone of any duration, it will be considered as recovery of hours, all the time.

data.name: RES_shifts.opcauseruledesc_38.rotext
data.value:
· If there is a delay in any zone of any duration, it will be considered as a delay at all times.
· If there is an early departure in any zone of any duration, it will be considered as an early departure at all times.
· If there is an excess in any zone of any duration, it will be considered as normal Extras at all times.

data.name: RES_shifts.opcauseruledesc_39.rotext
data.value:
· If there is a delay in any zone of any duration, it will be considered as a delay at all times.
· If there is an early departure in any zone of any duration, it will be considered as an early departure at all times.
· If there is an excess in any zone less than or equal to 00:29, it will be considered as Unprocessed Hours at all times.
· If there is an excess in any zone greater than or equal to 00:30, it will be considered as Normal Extras at all times.

data.name: RES_shifts.opcauseruledesc_40.rotext
data.value:
· If there is an absence in flexible hours in any zone of any duration, it will be considered as Hours to be recovered, all the time.
· If there is an excess in any zone of any duration, it will be considered as Recovery of hours, all the time.

data.name: RES_shifts.shifttypechange.partrigid2partsemiflex.rotext

· If there is an excess in any zone greater than or equal to 00:30, it will be considered as Normal Extras at all times.
